) AS [t] ON [s.AttestationUserBelts].[AttestationId] = [t].[Id]

INNER JOIN [Comissions] AS [s.Comission] ON [s].[ComissionId] = [s.Comission].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Regions] AS [s.Region] ON [s].[RegionId] = [s.Region].[Id]
ORDER BY [s].[Id]

SELECT [s.AttestationUserBelts].[AttestationId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[SportmanId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[BeltId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[Id]
FROM [AttestationUserBelts] AS [s.AttestationUserBelts]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [s0].[Id]
    FROM [Attestations] AS [s0]
    INNER JOIN [Comissions] AS [s.Comission0] ON [s0].[ComissionId] = [s.Comission0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Regions] AS [s.Region0] ON [s0].[RegionId] = [s.Region0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [s.AttestationUserBelts].[AttestationId] = [t].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]

Executed DbCommand (5ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']

Executing action method msac_tpa_new.Controllers.AttestationController.Index (msac-tpa-new) - Validation state: Valid
Executed DbCommand (14ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[Address], [s].[ComissionId], [s].[DescisionFilePath], [s].[IssueDate], [s].[OrderFilePath], [s].[RegionId], [s.Comission].[Id], [s.Comission].[Name], [s.Comission].[RegionId], [s.Region].[Id], [s.Region].[Name]
FROM [Attestations] AS [s]
INNER JOIN [Comissions] AS [s.Comission] ON [s].[ComissionId] = [s.Comission].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Regions] AS [s.Region] ON [s].[RegionId] = [s.Region].[Id]
ORDER BY [s].[Id]
Executed DbCommand (5ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [s.AttestationUserBelts].[AttestationId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[SportmanId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[BeltId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[Id]
FROM [AttestationUserBelts] AS [s.AttestationUserBelts]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [s0].[Id]
    FROM [Attestations] AS [s0]

FROM [AttestationUserBelts] AS [s.AttestationUserBelts]

    FROM [Attestations] AS [s0]

    INNER JOIN [Regions] AS [s.Region0] ON [s0].[RegionId] = [s.Region0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [s.AttestationUserBelts].[AttestationId] = [t].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]

Executed DbCommand (5ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [s.AttestationUserBelts].[AttestationId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[SportmanId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[BeltId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[Id]
FROM [AttestationUserBelts] AS [s.AttestationUserBelts]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [s0].[Id]
    FROM [Attestations] AS [s0]
    INNER JOIN [Comissions] AS [s.Comission0] ON [s0].[ComissionId] = [s.Comission0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Regions] AS [s.Region0] ON [s0].[RegionId] = [s.Region0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [s.AttestationUserBelts].[AttestationId] = [t].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]

FROM [AttestationUserBelts] AS [s.AttestationUserBelts]

    INNER JOIN [Comissions] AS [s.Comission0] ON [s0].[ComissionId] = [s.Comission0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Regions] AS [s.Region0] ON [s0].[RegionId] = [s.Region0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [s.AttestationUserBelts].[AttestationId] = [t].[Id]

SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM [SportMans] AS [s]
Executed DbCommand (96ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='0', @__p_1='5'], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[AvatarFilePath], [s].[BirthDay], [s].[LastName], [s].[Name], [s].[RegionId], [s].[Surname], [s.Region].[Id], [s.Region].[Name]
FROM [SportMans] AS [s]
INNER JOIN [Regions] AS [s.Region] ON [s].[RegionId] = [s.Region].[Id]
ORDER BY [s].[Surname], [s].[Id]
OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
Executed DbCommand (5ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='0', @__p_1='5'], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [s.AttestationUserBelts].[AttestationId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[SportmanId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[BeltId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[Id]
FROM [AttestationUserBelts] AS [s.AttestationUserBelts]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [s0].[Id], [s0].[Surname]
        FROM [SportMans] AS [s0]
        INNER JOIN [Regions] AS [s.Region0] ON [s0].[RegionId] = [s.Region0].[Id]
        ORDER BY [s0].[Surname], [s0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [s.AttestationUserBelts].[SportmanId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[Surname], [t0].[Id]

INNER JOIN [Regions] AS [s.Region] ON [s].[RegionId] = [s.Region].[Id]
ORDER BY [s].[Surname], [s].[Id]
OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_0 ROWS ONLY
Executed DbCommand (6ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='5'], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [s.AttestationUserBelts].[AttestationId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[SportmanId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[BeltId], [s.AttestationUserBelts].[Id]
FROM [AttestationUserBelts] AS [s.AttestationUserBelts]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [s0].[Id], [s0].[Surname]
        FROM [SportMans] AS [s0]
        INNER JOIN [Regions] AS [s.Region0] ON [s0].[RegionId] = [s.Region0].[Id]
        ORDER BY [s0].[Surname], [s0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_0 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [s.AttestationUserBelts].[SportmanId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[Surname], [t0].[Id]
